(a) AWS â€“ Organization & RBAC

    â— Make sure you have access to AWS Organizations, which is outside the free-tier. If not, do user creation and IAM roles instead.

Steps (Organization Creation)

    Login to AWS Console: https://console.aws.amazon.com/

    Go to AWS Organizations.

    Click Create Organization â†’ Choose Consolidated Billing or All Features.

    Add accounts: Create a new AWS account under this organization or invite an existing one.

    Set OU (Organizational Units) if needed for structure.

Steps (RBAC â€“ IAM Roles & Policies)

    Go to IAM â†’ Users â†’ Add user.

    Choose programmatic access or console access.

