âœ… 3. Create Alerts for Cloud Resource Usage
AWS â€“ Usage Alerts

    Go to CloudWatch â†’ Alarms.

    Create Alarm â†’ Select metric (e.g., CPU usage of EC2).

    Set threshold (e.g., CPU > 70%).

